// 3/2 connection case
// SAME FOR 4 connections, 5 connections
// Leader should be elected
// Leader should be able to append entries
// Client should be able to put data to leader
// Client should be able to get data from leader
// Logs up to the leader commit index should be identical on a majority of nodes
// Logs on all nodes should be identical or missing up to commit index
CREATE 0.0
PARTITION 3
1 2 3
4 0
SLEEP 500
STATE
ASSERT PARTITION
// ASSERT CLIENT_FUNCTIONALITY 
ASSERT LEADER_FUNCTIONALITY
ASSERT LOG_CONSISTENCY
